commitResults.messageBody:
Previously, the application was assuming that the format of the
import file was correct. This assumption could cause the
application to crash.

This commit adds functionality to check whether format of
file headers and rows are meets the requirements of the program.
This reverts commit 5ccc0e7598aba701534634cd5f2ab3a3e990d7b6.

Previously no exporting data to csv functionality

This commit will provide users with the option to export data
upon closing the application
